498
00:56:59,750 --> 00:57:00,750
DOC: Good evening.

499
00:57:00,835 --> 00:57:02,836
SZELL: I'm not one
to be mocked. Behave...

500
00:57:02,962 --> 00:57:04,879
DOC: Don't give me shit
about my behaviour.

501
00:57:04,964 --> 00:57:06,089
Not after what you've been pulling.

502
00:57:06,257 --> 00:57:09,259
- I've done nothing.
- So Chen acted on his own?

503
00:57:10,761 --> 00:57:14,806
I don't mind you hiring him,
but getting my brother involved?

504
00:57:14,890 --> 00:57:16,975
- It was nothing.
- It was a violation.

505
00:57:17,310 --> 00:57:19,728
We do not involve family, ever.

506
00:57:19,812 --> 00:57:22,814
Think of it as a warning. Nothing more.

507
00:57:23,232 --> 00:57:24,232
(GRUNTS)

508
00:57:25,318 --> 00:57:28,028
Think of that as a warning
and nothing more.

509
00:57:29,488 --> 00:57:32,073
SZELL: You'd like to fight, wouldn't you?

510
00:57:32,700 --> 00:57:34,534
It will not happen.

511
00:57:35,036 --> 00:57:37,912
I'm much too old
and far too smart for that.

512
00:57:38,372 --> 00:57:42,250
But we must talk. Truthfully.

513
00:57:43,544 --> 00:57:46,671
- Are you to be trusted?
- No.

514
00:57:49,842 --> 00:57:53,428
Is that the truth,
or are you trying again to upset me?

515
00:57:53,512 --> 00:57:56,931
- You'll go to the bank sooner or later.
- Perhaps I've already been.

516
00:57:57,016 --> 00:57:59,476
If so, you wouldn't be here with me.

517
00:57:59,560 --> 00:58:02,395
- What else do you know?
- I know you're panicking.

518
00:58:02,730 --> 00:58:06,232
- You think you'll get robbed.
- Who would do that?

519
00:58:06,317 --> 00:58:08,568
- Obviously, you think I would.
- Well?

520
00:58:09,737 --> 00:58:12,989
- Can I trust you?
- You never could. You only had to.

521
00:58:13,074 --> 00:58:15,408
We're talking of my safety.

522
00:58:16,410 --> 00:58:18,745
- May I be candid?
- Yes.

523
00:58:19,413 --> 00:58:22,165
I couldn't give a fuck about you...
(GASPS)

524
00:59:19,807 --> 00:59:21,224
(PHONE RINGING)

525
00:59:23,102 --> 00:59:24,978
Hello? Hi, Elsa.

526
00:59:25,062 --> 00:59:27,689
Are you all right? Did you get my note?

527
00:59:27,815 --> 00:59:31,359
I've been trying you for two hours.
Finally, I just went running.

528
00:59:31,902 --> 00:59:34,863
I'm sorry about your brother.

529
00:59:34,989 --> 00:59:37,282
- It doesn't matter.
- It does!

530
00:59:38,242 --> 00:59:40,368
I don't care. Forget it. It didn't happen.

531
00:59:40,453 --> 00:59:43,538
I wanted to explain.
I lied about the Swiss, because...

532
00:59:44,665 --> 00:59:46,458
(SPEAKING FRENCH)

533
00:59:49,128 --> 00:59:52,297
Take it easy, will you?
I can't understand.

534
00:59:53,841 --> 00:59:55,633
Let me come over.

535
00:59:55,718 --> 00:59:59,679
Okay? I'll take a shower, I'll be there?
